    Cart total

    The amount of the "Cart total" includes the discounts for the products on offer, except for the discounts reimbursed to your EROSKI club card. You can check the discounted amount in the section "Your savings".

    The amount may vary depending on: a. The exact weight of the fresh product, its price on the day of order delivery and its availability. If the product is not available, we will call you to make a proposal and tell you the new cost.

    b. The availability of the other products. If a product is not available and we replace it with another one, the difference in weight or size may mean a change in the total amount.
